ergenthaler exec vpcfo philippe krakowsky exec vpchief strategy officer christopher f carroll senior vpchief acctg ofcrcontroller show more homepage  ipg ipg about overview our leadership sustainability corporate governance contact us our agencies find an agency see the work ideas news investor relations overview  proxy materials news  events sec filings esg criteria stock information shareholder services careers overview job openings at ipg corporate ipg intern program community outreach  volunteering diversity overview programs results supplier diversity employee resource groups interpublic group is a global leader in modern marketing solutions with  diverse and talented individuals our companies drive business results for clients around the world see all agencies rga rga is a world leader in developing marketing solutions that help fortune  companies and worldclass brands build meaningful relationships with consumers in the digital age see our work media partnership because our expert teams blend backgrounds in general market buying direct print and digital we not only optimize media buys but also the media approach see our work rogers  cowan rogers  cowan is a leader in entertainment marketing and communications see our work mullenlowe group mullen lowe group is a creatively driven integrated marketing communications network with a strong entrepreneurial heritage and challenger mentality see our work deutsch we are a multidisciplinary agency with offices in ny and la known for our insatiable culture and ability to drive bottomline business results for clients see our work mccann with operations in over  countries and some eight decades of multinational experience mccann erickson has been recognized as the creator of the modern global advertising agency model see our work hackeragency hackeragency is a digitaldirect agency that helps you nail your marketing goals with programs that hit your target audience where they live work and play see our work orion orion trading ipgs barter organization enables some of the largest brands in the world to partfund media expenditures with their assets see our work devries global we are an agency with serious publicity chops strategic rigor and a long successful track record of disciplined account management for powerhouse global marketers and iconic consumer brands see our work fcb with an equal focus on creativity and accountability fcb is committed to producing brilliant ideas that change consumer behavior   see our work mccann worldgroup mccann worldgroup aligns the world’s largest advertising agency network mccann erickson with bestinclass specialty networks to provide complementary services transform clients brands and grow their businesses see our work pmk•bnc experts in enhancing talent and brand relationships with consumers and fans through passion points of entertainment sports music philanthropy art and fashion see our work rapport worldwide rapport is a global outofhome media planning and buying agency with a mission to build rapport between brands and their consumers   see our work film fashion film fashion a division of rogers  cowan matches fashion and accessory brands with prominent celebrities to provide heightened brand awareness see our work fcb health fcb health has one unique mission use the adaptation and application of key insights and techniques from the behavioral sciences to create brand building communications see our work the axis agency we specialize in developing communications that achieve breakthrough success for leading brands among hispanic and african american consumers learn how we combine insights strategy creativity and diversity to create campaigns that align with culturebased ideas see our work iw group iw group specializes in targeting the more than  million asianpacific americans in the us with annual spending clout that exceeds  billion see our work avrett free ginsberg while other agencies scramble to reverse engineer themselves for the age of collaboration afg was born with collaboration at its core see our work campbell ewald we create conversation shape it change it see our work octagon octagon worldwide is the recognized global thought leader in passionbased sports and entertainment content marketing see our work the martin agency one of the worlds most awarded creative agencies the martin agency has been bringing new energy to brands like walmart geico and oreo for more than  years see our work current with expertise in public relations content strategy and social media we create genuine connections between brands and people to change behavior and move brands forward see our work frank about women frank about women is a pioneering leader in marketing to women and turning insights into action for fortune  companies around the globe see our work tierney lets start a conversation we believe great brands are built by more than great ads were a fullservice communications agency that helps companies have a dialogue with their customers see our work advantage advantage international is a sponsorship and brand experience agency that specializes in strategic and creative solutions within the realm of sports entertainment and lifestyle experiences see our work hill holliday weve been helping clients fight and win the daily share battle since  see our work jack morton worldwide what we do is pretty simple we create experiences that strengthen relationships between brands and the people who matter most to them see our work prohealth illuminates the brand science we harness the most relevant data to build scientific narratives for products at all phases of their lifecycle see our work ipg mediabrands we were founded by ipg in  to manage all of its global mediarelated assets today that means we manage and invest  billion in global media see our work mrmmccann mrmmccann is a global customer experiencemarketing agency we simplify the complex—helping our clients navigate transform and gain competitive advantage within todays multidimensional digitallydriven world  see our work insidedge through years of experience insidedge has helped companies connect with their employees through effective internal communication see our work huge as a fullservice interactive agency huge is responsible for digital strategy and implementation for some of the largest companies and brands in the world see our work id media id media is known for identifying and delivering accountable media solutions that create better business outcomes for marketers see our work area  area  is a fullservice healthcare communications agency with a unique operating structure and innovative philosophy that make it uniquely brandfocused see our work carmichael lynch carmichael lynch has a history of creating powerful emotional connections to brands in creating these connections we do more than make our clients brands top of mind for their target we create a lasting bond between brands and people see our work um um has set out to prove that curiosity works a performancedriven agency with avid curiosity enthusiastic collaboration and resolute accountability at its core um breeds a culture of curious collaborative thinkers see our work neon neon is a unique synthesis of traditional and digital marketing experts who leverage insights data and analytics to successfully launch new products and increase growth for inline brands  see our work cassidy  associates founded in  cassidy  associates is a premier government relations firm with a solid foundation grounded in our history see our work pipeline ps we work with clients and agencies to quickly and costeffectively get their communications into the marketplace see our work fitzgerald  co any agency can create ads we believe our job is to create demand to create response to create results see our work initiative initiative believes that all marketing should be performancedriven see our work weber shandwick our success is built on deep commitment to client service our people creativity collaboration and harnessing the power of advocates  engaging stakeholders in new and creative ways to build brands and reputation see our work ipg media lab the ipg media lab is equal parts think tank realworld proving ground and change enabler see our work golin golin is a global integrated public relations and marketing communications firm dedicated to helping clients win in todays dynamic evolving marketplace see our work ipg news ipg announces second quarter and first half  results listen to the earnings webcast replay posted on july   um gaming giant ubisoft names um its us media agency of record posted on july   weber shandwick population services international psi india appoints weber shandwick india as communications partner posted on july   see all news  interpublic group  all rights reserved ipg  ipgaboutour agenciesideasnewsinvestor relationscareersdiversitycontact usterms of useprivacy noticesitemap interpublic group of companies  wikipedia interpublic group of companies from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search this article relies too much on references to primary sources please improve this by adding secondary or tertiary sources march  learn how and when to remove this template message interpublic group of companies type public traded as nyse ipg sp  component industry advertising agency predecessor mccannerickson inc founded   years ago  as mccann erickson   as interpublic group headquarters  third avenue new york ny  united states key people michael i roth chairman ceo  president revenue us  million   us  million   net income us  million   us  million   total assets us  million   us  million   total equity us  million   us  million   number of employees   as of april update website wwwinterpubliccom the interpublic group of companies inc ipg is a publicly traded advertising company the company consists of three major networks mccann worldgroup lowe and partners and fcb its media agencies are bundled under the ipg media