elevant – discuss on march   ipgs financial review process resulted in restatement of  interim periods and the recording of immaterial outofperiod adjustments to fourth quarter  financial resultsrelevant – discuss interpublic working to simplify its structure after its overload of deals in the s and s did not complete any acquisitions in  and citation needed it disposed of  businesses in  and  primarily outside the us interpublic said it exited  lossmaking international affiliates in  interpublic in april  announced it agreed to buy reprise media a search engine marketing firmcitation needed in july of that same year fcbulka advertising private limited a subsidiary of ipg was renamed draftfcbulka advertising pvt ltd companiesedit as of july  campbell ewald cassidy  associates deutsch inc fcb new name of draftfcb a merger of draft worldwide and foote cone  belding worldwide golin hill holliday huge jack morton worldwide the martin agency mccann mullenlowe profero octagon worldwide rga rogers  cowan tierney communications universal mccann mrmmccann uxus weber shandwick referencesedit  a b executive profile michael isor roth bloomberg business june     a b c d e f g h interpublic group of companies inc  annual report form k xbrl united states securities and exchange commission february     ipg about  ipg interpubliccom   agency family trees  interpublic group  ipg retrieved aug     the new york times advertisings big four its their world now   ipg company profile wall street journal retrieved    abbey gardy llp announces class action lawsuit against the interpublic group of companies inc and certain of its officers and directors  ipg september   retrieved jul     yahoo finance charts financeyahoocom retrieved    the interpublic group of companies inc expects to restate financial statements   interpublic earnings restatement finalized at  million   interpublic reports fourth quarter  results   interpublic to restate  profit   interpublic announces fourth quarter and ful