 vice president chief growth officer heide gardner senior vice president chief diversity  inclusion officer john halper senior vice president chief information officer richard j haray senior vice president corporate services joe kelly senior vice president talent peter leinroth senior vice president managing director jerome j leshne senior vice president investor relations terry peigh senior vice president managing director see our board of directors chairman and chief executive officer michael i roth michael i roth is chairman and ceo of interpublic nyse ipg one of the worlds largest organizations of advertising and marketing services companies prior to serving in his current role roth was a member of the company’s board of directors since assuming leadership of interpublic in  roth has righted the company’s financial course and moved to make it an industry leader by defining new models that provide value to clients in a rapidlychanging media and marketing environment prior to his current role roth was chairman and ceo of the mony group inc a financial services holding company under roths leadership the mony group diversified its business mix broadened its distribution channels and enhanced its ability to compete in a changing financial services marketplace roth is a member of the board of directors for pitney bowes inc the ad council and ryman hospitality properties he sits on the leadership committee of lincoln center for the performing arts the board of directors of the committee encouraging corporate philanthropy and the national center on addiction and substance abuse at columbia university casa in addition he is a director of the baruch college fund and the partnership for new york city he is also a member of the business roundtable and new yorkpresbyterian hospital’s heart steering committee a certified public accountant roth holds an llm degree from new york university law school and a jd from boston university law school he is a  graduate of the city college of new york view photos download image download image “ we’ve invested significantly in programs that position ipg as the employer of choice for our industry’s best and most diverse talent ” michael i roth in the press campaign michael roth ipg leads the way on creativity and integration april   fast company rga announces marketing tech venture studio in partnership with interpublic august   exchangemedia exchangemedia interviews michael roth at cannes  july   business insider business insider interviewed michael roth at advertising week europe april   barrons michael roth talks to barrons about ipgs recent successes and marketplace strategies march   bloomberg bloomberg radio interviews michael roth march   as as presidentceo nancy hill interviews michael roth at the as data summit  march   dircomfidencial dircomfidencial etrevista exclusiva michael roth january   michael roth discusses huge labs at advertising week kick off at iab mixx conference october   mm global michael roth in cannes its important to stay ahead of the curve july   the wall street journal cmo today michael roth in cannes creativity is still our industrys secret sauce june   michael roth moderates dialogue with verizons diego scotti at the the paley center april   beettv roth discusses the future of our industry april   informationweek roth on the importance of the free flow of data march   fox business opening bell roth discusses ipg and industry news with maria bartiromo february   cnbc squawk box michael roth on the state of advertising december   digital market asia michael roth delivers opening keynote at dmexco  september   cnbc mad money michael roth speaks with cnbcs jim cramer about ipgs second quarter earnings july   india’s exchangemedia roth on leadership ma and the local indian market july   barrons ceo spotlight michael roth june   bloomberg tv street smart roth discusses global ad trends july   mediapost roth mobile key to agency growth march   barrons like the jingles youll l