potential misconductrelevant – discuss on march   ipgs financial review process resulted in restatement of  interim periods and the recording of immaterial outofperiod adjustments to fourth quarter  financial resultsrelevant – discuss interpublic working to simplify its structure after its overload of deals in the s and s did not complete any acquisitions in  and citation needed it disposed of  businesses in  and  primarily outside the us interpublic said it exited  lossmaking international affiliates in  interpublic in april  announced it agreed to buy reprise media a search engine marketing firmcitation needed in july of that same year fcbulka advertising private limited a subsidiary of ipg was renamed draftfcbulka advertising pvt ltd companiesedit as of july  campbell ewald cassidy  associates deutsch inc fcb new name of draftfcb a merger of draft worldwide and foote cone  belding worldwide golin hill holliday huge jack morton worldwide the martin agency mccann mullenlowe profero octagon worldwide rga rogers  cowan tierney communications universal mccann mrmmccann uxus weber shandwick referencesedit  a b executive profile michael isor roth bloomberg business june     a b c d e f g h interpublic group of companies inc  annual report form k xbrl united states securities and exchange commission february     ipg about  ipg interpubliccom   agency family trees  interpublic group  ipg retrieved aug     the new york times advertisings big four its their world now   ipg company profile wall street journal retrieved    abbey gardy llp announces class action lawsuit against the interpublic group of companies inc and certain of its officers and directors  ipg september   retrieved jul     yahoo finance charts financeyahoocom retrieved    the interpublic group of companies inc expects to restate financial statements   interpublic earnings restatement finalized at  million   interpublic reports fourth quarter  results   interpublic to restate  profit   interpublic announces fourth quarter and fullyear  results   johnson bradley  april  no  interpublic group of cos adage retrieved  november    company overview of draftfcbulka advertising pvt ltd bloomberg businessweek retrieved    list of ipg agencies external linksedit official website business data for interpublic group of companies google finance yahoo finance reuters sec filings v t e interpublic group of companies campbell mithun cassidy  associates fcb golin harris international gotham hill holliday huge ipg mediabrands universal mccann jack morton worldwide jay advertising mccann worldgroup mccann erickson mrm worldwide mullen advertising octagon rga rogers  cowan the martin agency tm advertising weber shandwick retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleinterpublicgroupofcompaniesoldid categories companies established in advertising agencies of the united statescompanies based in new york citycompanies listed on the new york stock exchangeinterpublic groupholding companies of the united stateshidden categories articles lacking reliable references from march all articles lacking reliable referencespages using deprecated image syntaxarticles containing potentially dated statements from april all articles containing potentially dated statementswikipedia articles that may have offtopic sectionsall articles with unsourced statementsarticles with unsourced statements from may  navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portalrecent changescontact page tools what links hererelated changesupload filespecial pagespermanent linkpage informationwikidata itemcite this page printexport create a bookdownload as pdfprintable version languages deutschfrançaisromânăsuomi edit links this page was last edited on  july  at  text is availa